  <summary date="2019-08-09T14:36:59Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Survivors' Access to Supportive Care Act or SASCA

This bill establishes a series of programs and requirements to address the adequacy of access to sexual assault examinations, including a grant program for states to assess the availability of specified providers to perform sexual assault examinations.</summary>
